(!未鑑定の浮遊の指輪

?:[IOR [EQU $RACE High-Elf Golem Skeleton Zombie Spectre Archon] [AND [EQU $RACE Imp Balrog] [GEQ $LEVEL 10]] [AND [EQU $RACE Mindflayer] [GEQ $LEVEL 15]] [AND [EQU $RACE Dark-Elf] [GEQ $LEVEL 20]]]
# 透明視認持ち
